develop photos anymore, huh?

167
00:10:04,750 --> 00:10:05,830
Who is this?

168
00:10:06,450 --> 00:10:07,700
That's two people.

169
00:10:08,290 --> 00:10:09,200
Oh, right.

170
00:10:09,200 --> 00:10:11,660
