174
00:10:20,080 --> 00:10:21,370
I think so.

175
00:10:22,950 --> 00:10:24,410
So this is Jiang Tian?

176
00:10:25,040 --> 00:10:25,880
Mhm.

177
00:10:30,620 --> 00:10:32,580
And who's this man?

178
00:10:38,540 --> 00:10:39,660
Ji Huanyu.

179
00:10:44,200 --> 00:10:47,120
Ji Huanyu is truly a bad man.

180
00:10:48,620 --> 00:10:52,120
Tian had a tough time with him
when he was a child.

181
00:10:54,250 --> 00:10:56,750
Was Tian unhappy

182
