199
00:11:45,750 --> 00:11:47,700
or bother anyone.

200
00:11:58,200 --> 00:12:00,750
Back then, I had a cat named Commander.

201
00:12:00,750 --> 00:12:03,160
Sometimes when Tian couldn't go home,

202
00:12:03,160 --> 00:12:04,540
