203
00:12:04,540 --> 00:12:05,910
- at the door.
- What's your name?

204
00:12:05,910 --> 00:12:07,540
I took the chance

205
00:12:07,540 --> 00:12:08,790
to bring Tian to my house.

206
00:12:08,790 --> 00:12:10,290
- Can we be good friends?
- I let him in

207
00:12:10,290 --> 00:12:11,580
to get something to eat.

208
00:12:11,870 --> 00:12:13,790
I've been looking for my cat.

209
00:12:13,790 --> 00:12:15,620
So it's here with you.

210
00:12:16,120 --> 00:12:18,790
Grandpa, what's this cat's name?

211
00:12:18,790 --> 00:12:21,700
Its name is Commander. Does it sound nice?

212
00:12:21,700 --> 00:12:23,000
Yes.

213
00:12:24,410 --> 00:12:25,620
Why don't you go home?

214
00:12:25,620 --> 00:12:26,870
Isn't your grandma there?

215
00:12:31,370 --> 00:12:33,580
Do you wanna come over to my place?

216
00:12:33,790 --> 00:12:35,410
- Okay.
- Okay. Let's go.

217
00:12:35,410 --> 00:12:37,540
Hold it tight. I'll carry your bag.

218
00:12:39,410 --> 00:12:40,750
Are you hungry?

219
00:13:09,500 --> 00:13:11,950
Commander used to be a stray cat.

220
00:13:13,750 --> 00:13:15,910
He probably felt close to Commander

221
00:13:16,200 --> 00:13:18,250
because they were alike.

222
00:13:20,250 --> 00:13:21,450
Where is Commander now?

223
00:13:22,580 --> 00:13:23,540
It died.

224
00:13:24,750 --> 00:13:26,410
Commander lived outside.

225
00:13:27,040 --> 00:13:28,000
Tian

226
00:13:28,000 --> 00:13:30,080
often stayed outside,

227
00:13:30,080 --> 00:13:31,250
waiting for it.

228
00:13:32,290 --> 00:13:33,500
He told me

229
00:13:34,660 --> 00:13:37,410
as long as he waited there,
Commander would come back.

230
00:13:38,700 --> 00:13:40,120
But it never came back.

231
00:13:47,500 --> 00:13:49,370
It must have been hard for Ms. Jiang,

232
00:13:50,700 --> 00:13:52,410
to see Jiang Tian so lonely.

233
00:13:54,830 --> 00:13:56,540
