242
00:14:28,410 --> 00:14:30,370
I watched her grow up.

243
00:14:31,080 --> 00:14:33,370
She was hardworking and filial.

244
00:14:33,370 --> 00:14:35,290
She worked multiple jobs

245
00:14:35,290 --> 00:14:38,700
to pay her mom's medical bills
and raise Tian.

246
00:14:39,500 --> 00:14:42,620
She took on many side jobs in Taipei

247
00:14:43,910 --> 00:14:46,290
but had no time for Tian.

248
00:14:46,750 --> 00:14:48,500
She felt very guilty.

249
00:14:48,950 --> 00:14:51,450
Sometimes when she came back to see Tian,

250
00:14:51,450 --> 00:14:54,540
her eyes were swollen like walnuts.

251
00:14:56,660 --> 00:14:58,580
He really had a tough childhood.

252
00:14:59,830 --> 00:15:01,200
