267
00:15:45,200 --> 00:15:46,910
Tian came to my house.

268
00:15:46,910 --> 00:15:50,040
I noticed a burn on the back of his neck.

269
00:15:51,950 --> 00:15:53,410
A few days later,

270
00:15:53,410 --> 00:15:55,950
