271
00:15:57,250 --> 00:15:59,700
Later, his mother took him home.

272
00:16:00,370 --> 00:16:01,660
Not long after,

273
00:16:02,120 --> 00:16:04,330
she divorced Ji Huanyu.

274
00:16:06,200 --> 00:16:10,500
Could the scar on his neck be from Ji...

275
00:16:11,200 --> 00:16:12,790
I asked him that too.

276
00:16:13,040 --> 00:16:14,290
But he said no.

277
00:16:15,160 --> 00:16:16,290
I think he just

278
00:16:16,950 --> 00:16:19,200
didn't want to tell me the truth.

279
00:16:21,620 --> 00:16:22,910
That's how he is.

280
00:16:22,910 --> 00:16:24,080
He keeps everything

281
00:16:24,080 --> 00:16:25,410
to himself.

