00:16:28,330 --> 00:16:29,700
After that,

283
00:16:29,700 --> 00:16:32,080
I don't know what happened,

284
00:16:32,370 --> 00:16:33,830
but Tian started wandering around,

285
00:16:34,330 --> 00:16:36,540
staying wherever he could.

286
00:16:37,250 --> 00:16:39,580
I often saw him with his suitcase,

287
00:16:40,620 --> 00:16:42,870
staying here and there.

288
00:16:44,200 --> 00:16:46,040
He couldn't get close to anyone.

289
00:16:47,330 --> 00:16:49,000
No one could keep him.

290
00:16:49,620 --> 00:16:50,750
Jiang Tian!

291
00:16:56,250 --> 00:16:57,290
You...

292
00:16:57,950 --> 00:16:59,120
Why are you packed?

293
00:17:02,790 --> 00:17:04,040
I'm not packed.

294
00:17:04,540 --> 00:17:05,910
I just left it like this.

295
00:17:08,580 --> 00:17:09,750
No wonder

296
00:17:10,370 --> 00:17:12,870
his suitcase is always so neatly packed,

297
00:17:13,450 --> 00:17:14,950
like he's ready to leave at any moment.

298
00:17:15,000 --> 00:17:16,680
(Student Dormitory Application Form)
(Jiang Tian)

299
00:17:16,700 --> 00:17:19,000
(Jiang Ou)
Turns out, staying is hard

300
00:17:19,330 --> 00:17:20,910
(Parent's Signature)
for him.

301
00:17:21,950 --> 00:17:22,790
From now on,

302
00:17:23,330 --> 00:17:24,620
you'll have lunch with me,

303
00:17:24,620 --> 00:17:25,870
and I'll live with you.

304
00:17:27,450 --> 00:17:28,830
You'd better not regret it.

305
00:17:30,830 --> 00:17:31,950
I know I never will.

306
00:17:56,560 --> 00:17:58,980
(Unfussy Gao Tianyang)
Where are you? It's about time for roll call.

307
00:18:01,290 --> 00:18:03,250
Grandpa Ding, I'm leaving. I'm late.

308
00:18:03,750 --> 00:18:04,700
Okay.

309
00:18:05,870 --> 00:18:07,370
I'm about to start the roll call.

310
00:18:08,000 --> 00:18:08,870
Discipline monitor,

311
00:18:08,870 --> 00:18:10,660
check for phones, please.

312
00:18:10,660 --> 00:18:11,500
Okay.

313
00:18:11,500 --> 00:18:12,910
Everyone, put your phones away.

314
00:18:12,910 --> 00:18:14,370
I'm taking names now.

315
00:18:14,700 --> 00:18:15,540
Gao Tianyang.

316
00:18:15,550 --> 00:18:16,400
Here.

317
00:18:16,410 --> 00:18:17,450
Feng Xinhua.

318
00:18:17,700 --> 00:18:18,540
Here.

319
00:18:18,700 --> 00:18:19,280
Zhou Yueqiao.

320
00:18:19,280 --> 00:18:20,310
(Sticky note: Cover for me.)
Here.

321
00:18:20,330 --> 00:18:21,070
(I'll be right back.)
Here.

322
00:18:21,080 --> 00:18:22,160
Chen Dongxiang.

323
00:18:22,160 --> 00:18:22,480
Here.

324
00:18:22,480 --> 00:18:23,990
(I'll say you went to the health center.)
Gu Youjia.

325
00:18:23,990 --> 00:18:24,670
(Be quick.)
Gu Youjia.

326
00:18:24,670 --> 00:18:25,210
Here.

327
00:18:25,450 --> 00:18:26,580
Qi Jiahao.

328
00:18:28,250 --> 00:18:29,250
He's not here.

329
00:18:29,700 --> 00:18:31,040
Does anyone know where he is?

330
00:18:31,700 --> 00:18:33,030
Qi Jiahao has been missing a lot lately.

331
00:18:33,030 --> 00:18:34,160
- Why?
- I think I saw him with Zhai Tao

332
00:18:34,160 --> 00:18:36,290
heading towards Road No. 3.

333
00:18:36,500 --> 00:18:38,200
Okay. I'll write him down.

334
00:18:40,950 --> 00:18:42,040
Song Sirui.

335
00:18:42,040 --> 00:18:42,880
Here.

336
00:18:43,290 --> 00:18:44,290
Xu Tianshu.

337
00:18:44,950 --> 00:18:46,660
Really? What are they doing there?

338
00:18:46,660 --> 00:18:48,790
How could I know? Put your phone away.

339
00:18:49,080 --> 00:18:50,290
And I'll write you down.

340
00:18:51,580 --> 00:18:52,580
Jiang Tian.

341
00:18:55,620 --> 00:18:57,120
- Jiang Tian?
- He was just here.

342
00:19:01,080 --> 00:19:02,290
Does anyone know where he is?

343
00:19:02,290 --> 00:19:05,660
I think I saw him with Zhai Tao
heading towards Road No. 3.

344
00:19:14,720 --> 00:19:15,640
(Students' Building)

345
00:19:34,620 --> 00:19:35,620
Mr. Zhao.

346
00:19:35,620 --> 00:19:36,790
(Happiness)
Did you see Sheng Wang?

347
00:19:37,040 --> 00:19:38,950
Wang? No.

348
00:19:39,830 --> 00:19:42,830
But I did see those students
who gave him trouble before.

349
00:19:44,410 --> 00:19:45,290
Hey,

350
00:19:45,660 --> 00:19:47,250
you should be careful too.

351
00:19:47,250 --> 00:19:49,040
They might come after you

352
00:19:49,040 --> 00:19:51,410
since you reported them last time.

353
00:20:01,580 --> 00:20:02,540
What's wrong?

354
00:20:03,580 --> 00:20:05,000
Are you sure you didn't see Wang?

355
00:20:07,500 --> 00:20:08,580
Where is he?

356
00:20:10,580 --> 00:20:11,420
I should go.

357
00:20:13,080 --> 00:20:14,000
Hey, wait.

358
00:20:15,160 --> 00:20:16,620
What's going on?

359
00:20:41,250 --> 00:20:42,160
What are you doing here?

360
00:20:53,450 --> 00:20:54,290
Sheng Wang.

361
00:20:56,540 --> 00:20:58,700
Linzi, Xi, it's you guys.

362
00:20:58,700 --> 00:20:59,870
Have you seen Jiang Tian?

363
00:21:00,250 --> 00:21:01,410
Jiang Tian?

364
00:21:01,410 --> 00:21:03,370
He's probably napping in the classroom.

365
00:21:04,120 --> 00:21:04,960
What's wrong?

366
00:21:05,750 --> 00:21:07,200
Do you know about Jiang Tian's father?

367
00:21:08,450 --> 00:21:10,620
Oh, I know. He's Ji Huanyu.

368
00:21:10,830 --> 00:21:13,750
I saw him today at Old Man Ding's place.

369
00:21:18,120 --> 00:21:19,620
We can't let him find Jiang Tian.

370
00:21:20,000 --> 00:21:21,700
I'm worried he'll take Jiang Tian away.

371
00:21:22,290 --> 00:21:23,540
Ta-Take him away?

372
00:21:23,540 --> 00:21:24,500
To where?

373
00:21:24,500 --> 00:21:26,660
We saw him near
the Little White House yesterday.

374
00:21:26,660 --> 00:21:28,620
We think he's here looking for Jiang Tian.

375
00:21:29,410 --> 00:21:31,410
But no one knows exactly what he wants.

376
00:21:31,410 --> 00:21:33,620
Anyway, let's be on guard

377
00:21:33,620 --> 00:21:34,950
and protect Jiang Tian.

378
00:21:34,950 --> 00:21:36,450
Yeah. Got it.

379
00:21:36,450 --> 00:21:37,870
I'll keep an eye on him.

380
00:21:39,910 --> 00:21:41,500
Okay, you should go back and rest now.

381
00:21:44,450 --> 00:21:45,330
Bye.

382
00:21:45,330 --> 00:21:46,330
- Bye.
- Bye.

383
00:21:54,900 --> 00:21:56,910
(Unfussy Gao Tianyang)
Tian heard that Zhai Tao and Qi Jiahao

384
00:21:56,910 --> 00:21:57,810
were on Road No. 3,

385
00:21:58,020 --> 00:21:58,910
so he went to find you.

386
00:21:58,910 --> 00:21:59,750
Did you see him?

387
00:22:42,250 --> 00:22:45,290
(When I feel abandoned by the world)

388
00:22:45,910 --> 00:22:48,660
(and think nothing I do
will make a difference,)

389
00:22:49,540 --> 00:22:50,830
(I forget)

390
00:22:51,750 --> 00:22:55,040
(that someone with no place to call home)

391
00:22:57,330 --> 00:22:58,910
(is still trying so hard for me)

392
00:23:00,500 --> 00:23:02,290
(and giving his all)

393
00:23:03,200 --> 00:23:04,450
(to protect me.)

394
00:23:20,200 --> 00:23:21,120
What are you doing here?

395
00:23:25,410 --> 00:23:26,660
Where have you been?

396
00:23:27,040 --> 00:23:28,660
Do you know the roll call is over?

397
00:23:30,790 --> 00:23:31,910
From now on,

398
00:23:34,750 --> 00:23:36,330
I'll always be by your side.

399
00:23:42,450 --> 00:23:43,370
I mean it.

400
00:23:51,910 --> 00:23:53,190
Okay. Let's go...

401
00:23:55,790 --> 00:23:56,630
Let's go somewhere.

402
00:23:58,040 --> 00:23:59,620
Come on.

403
00:23:59,620 --> 00:24:00,620
Hey, where are you going?

404
00:24:00,620 --> 00:24:01,580
We can't get out now.

405
00:24:02,330 --> 00:24:03,170
Hey.

406
00:24:04,870 --> 00:24:06,000
What do you want?

407
00:24:08,450 --> 00:24:09,290
Climb over it.

408
00:24:11,950 --> 00:24:12,830
Why?

409
00:24:13,040 --> 00:24:14,290
Because...

410
00:24:14,290 --> 00:24:16,120
I've never skipped classes before.

411
00:24:16,870 --> 00:24:18,410
You haven't either, right?

412
00:24:20,580 --> 00:24:21,660
I've seen it happen.

413
00:24:21,660 --> 00:24:22,950
That doesn't count.

414
00:24:22,950 --> 00:24:25,410
Does watching a murder make you a killer?

415
00:24:25,870 --> 00:24:27,700
Oh, I find you really talented.

416
00:24:28,290 --> 00:24:30,700
You can connect totally unrelated things.

417
00:24:31,250 --> 00:24:33,160
And it's hard to argue with me,

418
00:24:33,160 --> 00:24:34,160
isn't it?

419
00:24:36,200 --> 00:24:37,540
- What are you doing?
- Run.

420
00:24:37,540 --> 00:24:38,500
What are you doing?

421
00:24:41,700 --> 00:24:42,660
Stop there!

422
00:24:43,450 --> 00:24:45,040
Which class are you from?

423
00:24:45,040 --> 00:24:45,950
Come back!

424
00:24:47,950 --> 00:24:49,040
Gao Tianyang.

425
00:24:49,500 --> 00:24:50,540
Yes, Jing.

426
00:24:51,660 --> 00:24:53,790
Where are Sheng Wang and Jiang Tian?

427
00:24:54,870 --> 00:24:57,120
Sheng Wang is in the health center.

428
00:24:58,120 --> 00:24:59,370
What about Jiang Tian?

429
00:24:59,370 --> 00:25:00,370
Oh. Jiang Tian.

430
00:25:01,450 --> 00:25:03,250
Well, Jiang Tian...

431
00:25:03,250 --> 00:25:05,790
Don't tell me he's in the health center too.

432
00:25:05,790 --> 00:25:06,750
It's a possibility.

433
00:25:06,750 --> 00:25:08,700
Jing, as I get older,

434
00:25:08,700 --> 00:25:10,160
I've realized

435
00:25:10,160 --> 00:25:11,410
that anything is possible.

436
00:25:12,870 --> 00:25:14,120
Impossible!

437
00:25:14,620 --> 00:25:16,870
I just called the health center.

438
00:25:16,870 --> 00:25:19,370
Sheng Wang and Jiang Tian are not there.

439
00:25:23,080 --> 00:25:24,370
(Sheng!)

440
00:25:24,370 --> 00:25:25,540
(Tian!)

441
00:25:25,870 --> 00:25:27,040
That's a good thing.

442
00:25:27,040 --> 00:25:29,160
It means they're healthy and have no issues.

443
00:25:29,160 --> 00:25:30,330
Clap, clap.

444
00:25:30,330 --> 00:25:31,330
That's good.

445
00:25:31,700 --> 00:25:33,330
Gao Tianyang.

446
00:25:33,870 --> 00:25:34,710
You,

447
00:25:35,290 --> 00:25:36,500
go to the back of the classroom

448
00:25:36,500 --> 00:25:37,660
and squat.

449
00:25:45,290 --> 00:25:47,250
Stay there and do the horse stance

450
00:25:47,250 --> 00:25:49,500
until Sheng Wang and Jiang Tian come back.

451
00:25:49,500 --> 00:25:50,580
Understood?

452
00:25:51,040 --> 00:25:52,000
Yes.

453
00:25:52,250 --> 00:25:53,290
Then do it now!

454
00:26:03,750 --> 00:26:05,660
Jing, I can't do it now.

455
00:26:05,660 --> 00:26:07,790
It might be considered indecent exposure.

456
00:26:07,790 --> 00:26:09,540
You wouldn't make me a criminal,
would you, Jing?

457
00:26:11,450 --> 00:26:12,750
So what?

458
00:26:12,750 --> 00:26:14,370
No one can see you at the back.

459
00:26:14,370 --> 00:26:15,580
Do it.

460
00:26:16,700 --> 00:26:18,080
Now.

461
00:26:18,280 --> 00:26:19,210
What a fool.

462
00:26:22,750 --> 00:26:24,700
Alright, everyone.

463
00:26:24,700 --> 00:26:26,370
Stop laughing.

464
00:26:26,370 --> 00:26:27,620
Stop looking at him.

465
00:26:28,290 --> 00:26:30,120
Now, open your English textbooks.

466
00:26:31,620 --> 00:26:33,450
Gao Tianyang,

467
00:26:33,450 --> 00:26:34,500
keep it there.

468
00:26:37,160 --> 00:26:38,910
Turn to page 180.

469
00:26:44,410 --> 00:26:45,330
Are you okay?

470
00:26:58,290 --> 00:26:59,500
As the saying goes,

471
00:27:00,200 --> 00:27:02,950
"Where you fall is
where you should lie down."

472
00:27:03,790 --> 00:27:05,250
Let's rest here for a while.

473
00:27:06,120 --> 00:27:07,330
What do you want?

474
00:27:08,620 --> 00:27:10,750
I ran so hard to escape security.

475
00:27:10,750 --> 00:27:12,160
We can't go back to school now.

476
00:27:12,540 --> 00:27:14,080
We might as well lie down here.

477
00:27:14,080 --> 00:27:15,290
Join me for a bit.

478
00:27:34,660 --> 00:27:35,620
Jiang Tian.

479
00:27:40,120 --> 00:27:41,700
Today, I suddenly feel like

480
00:27:42,870 --> 00:27:44,910
we're about the same age.

481
00:27:54,910 --> 00:27:56,200
Aren't you supposed to be resting?

482
00:27:56,200 --> 00:27:57,370
Why so much chatter?

483
00:28:07,500 --> 00:28:08,790
Where do you want to go later?

484
00:28:16,330 --> 00:28:17,450
I'll have to think about it.

485
00:28:18,580 --> 00:28:19,500
Okay.

486
00:28:28,020 --> 00:28:32,230
♪I don't know how
to keep you from being confused♪

487
00:28:32,790 --> 00:28:35,730
♪I thought you understood♪

488
00:28:36,290 --> 00:28:40,850
♪Everything I say seems redundant♪

489
00:28:41,960 --> 00:28:46,820
♪You're like a mischievous whisper♪

490
00:28:46,980 --> 00:28:50,830
♪Familiar yet incomprehensible♪

491
00:28:51,200 --> 00:28:54,470
♪Our world♪

492
00:28:54,600 --> 00:28:57,310
♪Is just 17♪

493
00:28:57,680 --> 00:29:02,380
♪The future is too far away♪

494
00:29:02,880 --> 00:29:08,770
♪Let's run forward and never look back♪

495
00:29:10,330 --> 00:29:11,870
- My turn.
- Okay. You go.

496
00:29:14,230 --> 00:29:18,470
♪I will run to you♪

497
00:29:18,660 --> 00:29:19,620
My turn, my turn.

498
00:29:19,620 --> 00:29:20,790
Next one.

499
00:29:21,500 --> 00:29:22,340
One, two.

500
00:29:22,910 --> 00:29:24,790
Yeah. Double kill.

501
00:29:24,790 --> 00:29:25,910
Yes!

502
00:29:26,000 --> 00:29:29,000
♪Is a burning wasteland♪

503
00:29:29,000 --> 00:29:33,280
♪Ignite it with youth♪

504
00:29:33,550 --> 00:29:38,550
♪We run forward and dye the sky red♪

505
00:29:38,820 --> 00:29:43,240
♪Don't regret♪

506
00:29:43,620 --> 00:29:47,830
♪Don't look back♪

507
00:30:00,510 --> 00:30:04,520
♪I don't know where it went wrong♪

508
00:30:04,840 --> 00:30:07,940
♪Even after many years♪

509
00:30:08,290 --> 00:30:12,260
♪I still can't keep you from leaving♪

510
00:30:12,350 --> 00:30:15,040
♪Hold tight to me♪

511
00:30:15,240 --> 00:30:20,130
♪The future is too far away♪

512
00:30:20,500 --> 00:30:27,500
♪Let's run together
and never let go of each other♪

513
00:30:37,040 --> 00:30:37,910
Hey, Jiang Tian.

514
00:30:38,580 --> 00:30:39,580
Look over there.

515
00:30:40,830 --> 00:30:43,080
Earlier, I said I wanted you
to stay home with the boys.

516
00:30:43,080 --> 00:30:45,410
I was too harsh,

517
00:30:45,410 --> 00:30:46,620
so I wanted to ask you out.

518
00:30:46,620 --> 00:30:47,500
What are they doing there?

519
00:30:47,500 --> 00:30:48,910
- I hope you didn't take it personally.
- No idea.

520
00:30:48,910 --> 00:30:50,410
I'm fine. Everything is good.

521
00:30:50,410 --> 00:30:52,000
Yeah. Weren't you worried earlier

522
00:30:52,000 --> 00:30:53,620
about Tian not adjusting well?

523
00:30:53,620 --> 00:30:55,540
Look how happy they are now.

524
00:31:02,450 --> 00:31:03,660
Then we...

525
00:31:03,660 --> 00:31:05,160
Don't you want to know what my mom...

526
00:31:05,160 --> 00:31:06,470
- No, your dad...
- Then we can relax a bit, right?

527
00:31:06,470 --> 00:31:07,450
No. Don't you want to know

528
00:31:07,450 --> 00:31:09,080
what they do on a date?

529
00:31:10,410 --> 00:31:11,290
I don't.

530
00:31:12,160 --> 00:31:13,040
Oh.

531
00:31:13,040 --> 00:31:14,410
- But I do.
- Yeah, yeah.

532
00:31:14,700 --> 00:31:15,700
But you know.

533
00:31:15,700 --> 00:31:18,000
I still feel like he hasn't

534
00:31:18,000 --> 00:31:20,080
shared his true feelings with me.

535
00:31:20,080 --> 00:31:21,250
Hey, Ou.

536
00:31:22,620 --> 00:31:24,370
That takes time.

537
00:31:24,370 --> 00:31:26,200
Some things can't be rushed.

538
00:31:27,000 --> 00:31:29,750
But there is one thing
that needs to be dealt with first.

539
00:31:29,750 --> 00:31:30,790
Like...

540
00:31:31,790 --> 00:31:32,910
What is it?

541
00:31:33,950 --> 00:31:35,660
Like...

542
00:31:35,660 --> 00:31:38,200
Our family matters and future plans.

543
00:31:39,040 --> 00:31:41,120
Like our... Our mar...

544
00:31:41,500 --> 00:31:44,330
Oh, I get it. You are talking about money.

545
00:31:44,330 --> 00:31:46,200
With more people in the family,

546
00:31:46,200 --> 00:31:48,160
we need to save up, right?

547
00:31:49,540 --> 00:31:50,660
My dad is stupid.

548
00:31:51,250 --> 00:31:52,660
I'll set up a romantic atmosphere for him.

549
00:31:52,660 --> 00:31:53,580
Hey.

550
00:31:56,790 --> 00:31:57,950
Don't mess around.

551
00:32:02,580 --> 00:32:03,620
Ou.

552
00:32:07,040 --> 00:32:08,080
Marry me.

553
00:32:08,370 --> 00:32:09,330
He proposed.

554
00:32:11,620 --> 00:32:12,460
Dad...

555
00:32:14,250 --> 00:32:15,120
What are you doing?

556
00:32:16,140 --> 00:32:22,270
(Men's Room)

557
00:32:22,290 --> 00:32:23,370
Gao Tianyang.

558
00:32:23,370 --> 00:32:24,370
Are you done yet?

559
00:32:24,370 --> 00:32:25,540
Wait a second.

560
00:32:25,540 --> 00:32:26,910
Hurry up.

561
00:32:33,750 --> 00:32:34,830
Go in there.

562
00:32:37,370 --> 00:32:38,210
Thanks.

563
00:32:39,040 --> 00:32:41,620
I'm just showing some sympathy for you.

564
00:32:41,620 --> 00:32:42,580
No need to thank me.

565
00:32:43,290 --> 00:32:47,120
So, if I manage to get your sympathy,

566
00:32:47,120 --> 00:32:48,370
can I ask for your help?

567
00:32:49,370 --> 00:32:50,410
Sure.

568
00:32:50,410 --> 00:32:52,410
But you'll have to be even dumber than today.

569
00:32:54,000 --> 00:32:55,540
Oh, too bad.

570
00:32:55,540 --> 00:32:56,870
You might not be able to help me anymore.

571
00:32:58,200 --> 00:32:59,950
Do you even know yourself?

572
00:32:59,950 --> 00:33:01,620
Clearly, you have chances

573
00:33:01,620 --> 00:33:03,330
every day at any time.

574
00:33:03,330 --> 00:33:04,910
Every day at any time...

575
00:33:15,620 --> 00:33:16,460
Alright.

576
00:33:17,000 --> 00:33:19,540
I'll tell Sheng you're really kind

577
00:33:19,540 --> 00:33:20,540
and virtuous.

578
00:33:21,370 --> 00:33:23,450
Why... why would you tell him that?

579
00:33:23,830 --> 00:33:25,700
Maybe I'll tell Tian instead.

580
00:33:26,120 --> 00:33:28,040
But Sheng will never know

581
00:33:28,040 --> 00:33:29,950
how virtuous and adorable

582
00:33:29,950 --> 00:33:31,200
our Little Pepper is.

583
00:33:32,410 --> 00:33:33,330
You...

584
00:33:33,910 --> 00:33:34,750
What?

585
00:33:35,120 --> 00:33:36,540
Get in there.

586
00:33:40,830 --> 00:33:43,160
If you want to, just go tell him.

587
00:34:00,250 --> 00:34:02,700
Magic bracelets! Come and see!

588
00:34:03,250 --> 00:34:04,750
Feel free to check them out!

589
00:34:04,750 --> 00:34:06,790
Come and see, boys.

590
00:34:08,330 --> 00:34:09,620
- Hey, sir.
- Yes?

591
00:34:09,620 --> 00:34:11,250
Does this bracelet have any special meaning?

592
00:34:11,250 --> 00:34:13,750
Once you wear this bracelet,

593
00:34:13,750 --> 00:34:15,910
it ensures that the bond between family,
friends,

594
00:34:15,910 --> 00:34:18,250
or lovers will last forever.

595
00:34:18,250 --> 00:34:19,330
Feel it.

596
00:34:21,520 --> 00:34:22,370
Let me see.

597
00:34:22,370 --> 00:34:23,450
Sure, go ahead.

598
00:34:25,870 --> 00:34:26,750
Sir,

599
00:34:27,410 --> 00:34:28,250
I'll take these two.

600
00:34:29,790 --> 00:34:31,080
Good choice.

601
00:34:31,080 --> 00:34:33,410
I hope your bond lasts forever.

602
00:34:39,750 --> 00:34:40,790
What are you looking at?

603
00:34:42,290 --> 00:34:43,660
Watching them clean.

604
00:34:45,410 --> 00:34:46,950
What's so interesting about that?

605
00:34:47,410 --> 00:34:48,500
It's youth.

606
00:34:49,870 --> 00:34:51,200
Once you grow up,

607
00:34:51,660 --> 00:34:52,540
you can't go back.

608
00:34:57,620 --> 00:34:59,120
Zhao Xi.

609
00:34:59,950 --> 00:35:01,080
Jenny Yang.

610
00:35:01,500 --> 00:35:03,790
So, how does it feel to be back teaching?

611
00:35:03,790 --> 00:35:04,830
What do you think?

612
00:35:04,830 --> 00:35:06,290
Not bad, right?

613
00:35:06,660 --> 00:35:08,000
Thanks for your help.

614
00:35:08,160 --> 00:35:09,120
Not at all.

615
00:35:10,870 --> 00:35:14,370
Is this the friend you mentioned
meeting abroad?

616
00:35:14,370 --> 00:35:15,500
Aren't you going to introduce us?

617
00:35:16,830 --> 00:35:19,500
This is Lin from the History Department.

618
00:35:20,000 --> 00:35:22,000
Hi, I'm Yang Jing.

619
00:35:22,000 --> 00:35:23,000
I teach English.

620
00:35:23,000 --> 00:35:24,290
You can call me Jenny.

621
00:35:24,290 --> 00:35:25,250
Jenny.

622
00:35:25,870 --> 00:35:27,410
Hi, I'm Benny.

623
00:35:28,080 --> 00:35:30,160
How are you holding up at school?
All good?

624
00:35:31,500 --> 00:35:32,450
Not bad.

625
00:35:32,450 --> 00:35:33,290
That's good to hear.

626
00:35:34,200 --> 00:35:35,910
I'll get going now.

627
00:35:35,910 --> 00:35:37,080
If you need anything,

628
00:35:37,080 --> 00:35:38,410
just reach out to me.

629
00:35:38,410 --> 00:35:39,870
- See you.
- Okay, thanks.

630
00:35:39,870 --> 00:35:40,710
Bye.

631
00:35:44,830 --> 00:35:47,080
You seem to know Jenny pretty well.

632
00:35:47,410 --> 00:35:48,910
She's my high school classmate.

633
00:35:49,250 --> 00:35:52,410
After I came back from abroad,
she's the only one I've kept in touch with.

634
00:35:53,080 --> 00:35:55,580
I came back to be a substitute teacher
because of her.

635
00:35:56,300 --> 00:35:57,500
Does that count as knowing her well?

636
00:35:58,870 --> 00:35:59,910
Yeah.

637
00:36:16,250 --> 00:36:17,290
Pickled mangoes.

638
00:36:18,580 --> 00:36:20,410
They're sweet and sour, my childhood favorite.

639
00:36:20,700 --> 00:36:22,950
I rarely ate them after moving to Shanghai.

640
00:36:29,790 --> 00:36:31,790
Good food is best shared with good friends.

641
00:36:32,080 --> 00:36:33,040
Have one.

642
00:36:34,500 --> 00:36:35,540
Come on, have one.

643
00:36:35,540 --> 00:36:36,540
I don't eat snacks.

644
00:36:51,580 --> 00:36:52,830
You're a picky eater,

645
00:36:54,950 --> 00:36:56,250
but you like this?

646
00:36:58,160 --> 00:36:59,250
It's delicious.

647
00:36:59,950 --> 00:37:00,790
Oh, right.

648
00:37:01,160 --> 00:37:03,040
Why did you drag me away just now?

649
00:37:03,040 --> 00:37:04,910
I missed my dad's grand proposal.

650
00:37:07,450 --> 00:37:09,410
I was afraid you'd ruin their big moment.

651
00:37:10,290 --> 00:37:11,370
Nonsense.

652
00:37:12,830 --> 00:37:14,200
I was going to help them out

653
00:37:14,540 --> 00:37:16,330
by making some bubbles around

654
00:37:16,660 --> 00:37:17,950
and singing a little song.

655
00:37:18,580 --> 00:37:20,790
My dad was so clumsy when he proposed.

656
00:37:20,790 --> 00:37:21,750
It was driving me crazy.

657
00:37:33,370 --> 00:37:34,330
But...

658
00:37:35,580 --> 00:37:37,700
If my dad's proposal works out,

659
00:37:38,620 --> 00:37:40,080
we'll be brothers.

660
00:37:42,450 --> 00:37:43,620
Would that bother you?

661
00:37:57,040 --> 00:37:58,200
Help me with this.

662
00:37:59,040 --> 00:38:00,040
I want this one.

663
00:38:00,040 --> 00:38:01,250
I'll help you tie that one later.

664
00:38:07,750 --> 00:38:09,080
You know what?

665
00:38:09,080 --> 00:38:10,580
I've always felt

666
00:38:11,330 --> 00:38:14,790
that Mount Guanyin by the Tamsui River
is very spiritual.

667
00:38:15,200 --> 00:38:17,000
If you make a sincere wish there,

668
00:38:18,040 --> 00:38:19,370
it will come true.

669
00:38:23,620 --> 00:38:24,580
Here.

670
00:38:44,200 --> 00:38:45,160
So,

671
00:38:46,950 --> 00:38:48,120
let's live in the dorm together.

672
00:38:49,410 --> 00:38:50,410
You and I,

673
00:38:51,040 --> 00:38:51,880
together.

674
00:38:56,910 --> 00:38:57,750
Why?

675
00:38:59,870 --> 00:39:02,410
Because it will be a place that's truly yours,

676
00:39:02,790 --> 00:39:03,630
won't it?

677
00:39:04,000 --> 00:39:05,250
A true home.

678
00:39:07,950 --> 00:39:09,540
Instead of moving

679
00:39:09,540 --> 00:39:11,000
between Dad's,

680
00:39:11,000 --> 00:39:12,540
Mom's, and Ola Man Ding's,

681
00:39:13,290 --> 00:39:16,950
never knowing when to unpack

682
00:39:16,950 --> 00:39:18,080
or repack,

683
00:39:19,500 --> 00:39:20,700
living in the dorm

684
00:39:21,620 --> 00:39:23,120
is the most reassuring choice.

685
00:39:24,200 --> 00:39:26,250
Though we can't live in the dorm forever,

686
00:39:26,580 --> 00:39:29,080
it'll give you a clear timeline

687
00:39:29,950 --> 00:39:33,000
and a place that feels like yours,

688
00:39:33,000 --> 00:39:34,750
with a real sense of security and belonging.

689
00:39:35,950 --> 00:39:37,200
You'll like it, right?

690
00:39:42,750 --> 00:39:43,950
So, I'll be

691
00:39:44,250 --> 00:39:45,160
with you.

692
00:39:51,290 --> 00:39:52,130
Okay.

693
00:39:57,500 --> 00:39:58,500
You know,

694
00:39:58,500 --> 00:40:01,540
I secretly read in your Guide
to Lyrical Writing

695
00:40:01,540 --> 00:40:03,370
that holding someone like this

696
00:40:04,080 --> 00:40:05,790
means we're friends.

697
00:40:05,790 --> 00:40:07,870
But I think we're more than friends.

698
00:40:10,120 --> 00:40:11,250
We're family.

699
00:40:24,000 --> 00:40:26,290
Has Big Mouth Xu always been
called that since he was young?

700
00:40:27,040 --> 00:40:29,830
His mouth was big when he was young.

701
00:40:29,830 --> 00:40:31,450
But we used to call him Little Mouth Xu.

702
00:40:32,870 --> 00:40:34,250
Do you guys call him Big Mouth Xu?

703
00:40:34,950 --> 00:40:35,950
Not really.

704
00:40:36,830 --> 00:40:39,370
At least not in public.

705
00:40:39,370 --> 00:40:41,040
But we did call his son Little Mouth Xu.

706
00:40:46,700 --> 00:40:48,330
- Eat more.
- Have some veggies.

707
00:40:48,580 --> 00:40:50,290
- Delicious.
- Don't be picky.

708
00:40:50,870 --> 00:40:52,370
Wang, here.

709
00:40:54,870 --> 00:40:56,000
Give me some, too.

710
00:40:56,750 --> 00:40:58,250
Sure. I won't leave you out.

711
00:40:58,370 --> 00:40:59,290
Thanks.

712
00:41:09,540 --> 00:41:10,790
Eat more.

713
00:41:11,160 --> 00:41:12,000
You should, too.

714
00:41:12,000 --> 00:41:13,410
You need energy for your exams.

715
00:41:14,830 --> 00:41:15,670
Dad.

716
00:41:17,910 --> 00:41:19,500
Why did you call me Dad?

717
00:41:19,500 --> 00:41:21,040
Don't you usually call me Old Sheng?

718
00:41:21,450 --> 00:41:22,370
What's wrong?

719
00:41:22,620 --> 00:41:25,830
We have something to tell you.

720
00:41:31,040 --> 00:41:32,000
- Mom.
- Dad.

721
00:41:32,000 --> 00:41:33,990
- We'll live together in the dorm.
- We'll live together in the dorm.

722
00:41:38,540 --> 00:41:39,750
- In the dorm?
- In the dorm?

723
00:41:40,620 --> 00:41:41,910
What a joke.

724
00:41:41,910 --> 00:41:43,660
Why live at school when you have a home?

725
00:41:44,790 --> 00:41:45,630
I forbid it.

